    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** In this file we show that the fundamental group of a bouquet of circles indexed by a type S is the free group on that type S. We begin by defining S-indexed wedges of circles as the suspension of the pointification of S. *)\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Section AssumeUnivalence.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
